item.description: Looking forward to the review of the new kiseido book! Good job really forcing yourself to keep to the training instead of thinking "I have so much else to do, I'll do go-stuff tomorrow"!. note that the link to Dave Peck's Go Site is broken.

Looking forward to the review of the new kiseido book! Good job really forcing yourself to keep to the training instead of thinking “I have so much else to do, I’ll do go-stuff tomorrow”!.
